      <section class="social-media-presentation">

        <h2>Why Do You Need an Advertising Expert?</h2>

        <p>If you are an inexperienced advertiser, it will be difficult to create a profitable advertising campaign. First of all, you lack the experience to know what works. Secondly, you don’t not know what it takes to build a funnel that converts.</p>
        
        <p>At conversiongetter, we build funnels with measurable steps, designed to build the tension people should feel from the absence of your product/service.</p>

        <p>To move people through our funnels, we incorporate advertising, lead magnets, landing pages, retargeting, and email marketing. Each campaign is carefully planned, analyzed, and optimized to get the best possible result at the lowest cost.</p>

        <button class="quote-btn">GET QUOTE</button>
        <button class="our-process-btn">OUR PROCESS</button>
        

